        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Tanya:</b> Mango."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Andy:</b> Mango? Are they"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "out of one's mind",
              "word": "out of their minds"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "? Do they know how tough that is?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Tanya:</b> Yeah, but I told them we'd"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "take a crack at something",
              "word": "take a crack at it"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". If we"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "put one's mind to something",
              "word": "put our minds to it"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ", I know we can do it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Andy:</b> I don't know. It's not going to be easy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Tanya:</b> Let's"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "roll up one's sleeves",
              "word": "roll up our sleeves "
            },
            {
              "textEn": "and"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "give it one's best shot",
              "word": "give it our best shot"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "."
            },
            {
              "keyword": "nothing ventured, nothing gained",
              "word": "Nothing ventured, nothing gained"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>John:</b> Well, Tanya, you certainly have a"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "can-do attitude",
              "word": "can-do attitude"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Tanya:</b> Actually, this is"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "child's play",
              "word": "child's play"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "compared to what our CEO wants us to do by the end of the year. He wants us to come up with new, improved formulas for all 50 of our shampoos."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Andy:</b> What? How are we supposed to manage that? Sometimes I think the"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "bigwig",
